-TLwGUv3EPHfknjDYrjD\" target=\"https://zhidao.baidu.com/question/_blank\"><span style=\";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:windowtext;text-underline:none\">琼州学院学报</span></a><span style=\";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">.2008,15(2):39-41.</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\"> [4]Vaquero&nbsp;LM;Merino&nbsp;LR;Caceres&nbsp;J.&nbsp;A&nbsp;break&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;clouds:towards&nbsp;a&nbsp;cloud&nbsp;definition&nbsp;2009.(01</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\"><br/></span></p><p><br/></p>',379,169,2019),(30,'<p style=\"text-indent:37px;line-height:125%\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:125%;font-family: 宋体\">论文研究内容：</span></p><p style=\"line-height:125%\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体\">基于WIFI探针的商业大数据分析技术，其中包括：</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体\">搭建</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:125%\">R</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体\">语言</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:125%\">+Hadoop </span><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体\">离线计算平台环境、分析用户数据，设计并实现门前人流量、进店客流量、进入跳出量、新老顾客数量及新增量等离线计算模型、模型的可视化展示、系统构建、界面模型设计数据采集。界面模型功能如下：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">）客流量：店铺或区域整体客流及趋势</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 37px\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">）入店量：进入店铺或区域的客流及趋势</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 37px\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">）入店率：进入店铺或区域的客流占全部客流的比例及趋势</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 37px\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">）来访周期：进入店铺或区域的顾客距离上次来店的间隔</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 37px\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">）新老顾客：一定时间段内首次/两次以上进入店铺的顾客</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 37px\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">）顾客活跃度：按顾客距离上次来访间隔,划分为不同活跃度（高活跃度、中活跃度、低活跃度、沉睡活跃度）</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 37px\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">）驻店时长：进入店铺的顾客在店内的停留时长</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 37px\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">）跳出率：进入店铺后很快离店的顾客及占比(占总体客流)</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 37px\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">9</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">）深访率：进入店铺深度访问的顾客及占比(占总体客流)&nbsp; </span></p><p style=\"line-height:125%\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体\">论文研究要求：</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:37px\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">综合运用大学所学的《软件工程</span><span style=\"font-size:19px\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">》、《</span><span style=\"font-size:19px\">Javaee</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">程序设计》、《数据库原理》等课程知识以及通过其他技术性书籍完成下述要求：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:19px\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">．查找或阅读某方面的资料、文献等</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:19px\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">．做好完成作品所需的技术准备</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:19px\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">．完成</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">基于WIFI探针的商业大数据分析技术</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">作品，并在编写代码、书写文档等方面具备实际应用能力</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:19px\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">．按时参加毕业设计小组讨论</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:19px\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">．提交满足梧州学院工科毕业设计所要求的论文及作品</span></p><p><br/></p>','<p style=\"text-indent:37px;line-height:125%\"><span style=\"fon