yle=\"font-size:19px\">,2011.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:19px\">[7] </span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">何新起</span><span style=\"font-size:19px\">.</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">网站设计开发维护推广从入门到精通</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px\">[M].</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">北京</span><span style=\"font-size:19px\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体\">人民邮电出版社</span><span style=\"font-size:19px\">,2016.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:19px\">[8] Magdalena Wójcik. The Use of Web 2.0 Services by Urban Public Libraries in Poland: Changes over the Years 2011–2013[J]. Libri,2015,65(2):91-103.&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>',407,199,2019),(63,'<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体\">本课题研究的内容是贵港市港北区志鉴工作平台的设计与实现。本系统是基于</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">MVC</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体\">分层设计思想设计开发的，其中后台开发技术主要在采用主流的框架技术</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">SSH(Struts2+Spring 3.x+Hibernate 4.x)</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体\">；前端技术主要采用</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">Ajax+Jquery web2.0</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体\">技术，后台数据库是</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">Mysql5.6.x</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">FastDFS</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体\">分布式文件服务器对文件进行存储管理。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体\">本课题研究的内容有以下几个方面：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:0;text-indent:34px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体\">文件存储管理，系统使用</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">FastDFS+Nginx</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体\">服务器存储文件。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:0;text-indent:34px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体\">目录体系管理，系统管理员对目录进行分类。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:0;text-indent:34px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体\">目录任务管理，系统管理员指派目录任务给各个单位部门。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:0;text-indent:34px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">4.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体\">单位材料管理，单位完成管理员指派的目录任务，提交材料。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:0;text-indent:34px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">5.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体\">材料审核处理，专家审核单位上传的材料。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:0;text-indent:34px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">6.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体\">质量评估，管理员对专家和单位完成任务的情况进行评估。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:0;text-indent:34px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">7.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体\">系统管理，系统管理员给用户分配权限，对系统基本设置与管理。</span></p><p><br/></p>','<p style=\"margin-left:28px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">收集相关资料和文献，进行论文可行性评估。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">2.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">通过阅读文献与资料，了解相关的分布式文件系统的技术。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">3.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: nor